<div class="col-md-6">
<h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family font-choco">Jewellery for Short Hair</h2>
<p class="text-font-family font-choco">Short hair can provide a great opportunity to showcase your earrings and necklaces. For earrings, consider wearing studs or small hoops to accentuate your facial features. A simple pendant necklace or choker can also work well with short hair, drawing attention to your neck and collarbone. Check out Cassiopeia's <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/products/amethyst-silver-stud-earrings?_pos=2&amp;_psq=amethyst%20stud&amp;_ss=e&amp;_v=1.0">Amethyst Classic Silver Set Stud</a> or <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/products/blue-copper-turquoise-stud-earrings?_pos=5&amp;_psq=blue%20copper&amp;_ss=e&amp;_v=1.0">Blue Copper Turquoise Stud Earrings</a> for the perfect complement to a pixie cut.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div style="background-image: url('//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0620/0193/8600/files/image11.jpg?v=1680418078');" class="background-image top6"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row align-center mb-top">
<div class="col-md-6">
<h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family"><a href="#" class="font-choco">Physical Benefits of Wearing Moonstone</a></h2>
<p class="text-font-family font-choco">Moonstone is said to possess numerous physical benefits, such as promoting hormonal balance and supporting reproductive health. It is often used to alleviate menstrual discomfort and promote fertility. Wearing moonstone may also help improve digestion and boost the immune system, leading to overall better physical health.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div style="background-image: url('//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0620/0193/8600/files/image8.png?v=1680418110');" class="background-image top6"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row align-center mb-top">
<div class="col-md-6">
<h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family"><a href="#" class="font-choco">Jewellery for Shoulder Length Hair</a></h2>
<p class="text-font-family font-choco">Shoulder-length hair can be a versatile length that allows you to wear a variety of jewellery styles. For earrings, try dangle earrings to add some drama to your look. A delicate chain necklace with a small pendant can also work well with shoulder-length hair. Check out the Cassiopeia Gems <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/products/larimar-leaf-rhodium-rhodium-silver-earrings?_pos=2&amp;_sid=755975395&amp;_ss=r">Feather Earrings</a> and the <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/shop-rings/products/larimar-buffalo-black-horn-pendant-with-leather-chain">Larimar Trinity Pendant!</a></p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div style="background-image: url('//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0620/0193/8600/files/image9.png?v=1680418134');" class="background-image top6"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row align-center mb-top">
<div class="col-md-6">
<h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family"><a href="#" class="font-choco">Jewellery for Long Hair</a></h2>
<p class="text-font-family font-choco">Long hair can provide a great canvas for bold and statement jewellery pieces. Dangle earrings, hoops, and chandelier earrings can all work well with long hair, adding some extra sparkle and drama. For necklaces, consider wearing a <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/signature-necklace">signature necklace</a> or a <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/shop-rings">pendant necklace</a> to add some interest to your look. Cassiopeia's <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/larimar/products/gold-plated-larimar-necklace">blue stone necklaces</a> and <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/shop-rings/products/blue-copper-turquoise-silver-pendant">blue copper turquoise silver pendant</a> are ideal for long hair.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div style="background-image: url('//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0620/0193/8600/files/image6_cbb0ac24-a0e2-4c6f-9643-fd28c541569f.jpg?v=1680418158');" class="background-image top6"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row align-center mb-24">
<div class="col-md-6">
<h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family"><span class="font-brown mb-18">Matching Jewellery:</span> <a href="#" class="font-choco">1. With Hair Down</a></h2>
<p class="text-font-family font-choco">When wearing your hair down, earrings can help to accentuate your facial features and draw attention to your face. Small stud earrings or delicate drop earrings work well with long, loose hair. If you're looking to add some extra sparkle, try wearing statement earrings with a bold design or a pop of colour. Check out Cassiopeia's <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/silver-classic-set/products/moonstone-silver-classic-set">Moonstone Classic Silver Set</a> and the <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/products/amethyst-stud-earrings?_pos=1&amp;_psq=amethyst%20stud&amp;_ss=e&amp;_v=1.0">Amtheyst Stud Earrings</a> for some beautiful options.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div style="background-image: url('//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0620/0193/8600/files/image2_e9e12364-7944-4395-b3b3-97bd39ed2d62.jpg?v=1680418189');" class="background-image top6"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row align-center mb-top">
<div class="col-md-12">
<h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family"><a href="#" class="font-choco">2. With Updo Hairstyles</a></h2>
<p class="text-font-family font-choco">With an updo hairstyle, you have the opportunity to showcase bold and statement jewellery yet oftentimes, less is more without the addition of long locks. Simple hoop earrings or bold stud earrings can all add some dimension to your look. Consider choosing earrings that complement the colour or style of your outfit. For earrings, check out Cassiopeia’s <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/shop-earrings/products/citrine-cut-stud-earrings">Citrine Cut Stud Earrings</a> and for necklaces, you can’t go wrong with a <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/signature-necklace/products/solaire">Solaire</a> or <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/signature-necklace/products/ra-eye-with-white-topaz">Ra Eye with White Topaz</a> signature necklace.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row align-center mb-top">
<div class="col-md-12">
<h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family"><a href="#" class="font-choco">Matching Necklaces with Different Hairstyles</a></h2>
<p class="text-font-family font-choco mb-18">When choosing necklaces to match your hairstyle, consider the length and style of your necklace. A simple pendant necklace or choker can work great with short hair, while a long pendant necklace can complement long hair. For shoulder length hair, consider wearing a delicate chain necklace with a small pendant, or layering necklaces of different lengths. With an updo hairstyle, try wearing a bold statement necklace or a layered necklace.</p>
<p class="text-font-family font-choco">Choosing the right jewellery to match your hairstyle can enhance your overall look and complement your outfit. From delicate studs to bold statement pieces, there are jewellery options that can work with any hairstyle. By considering the length and style of your hair, you can choose the perfect earrings and necklaces to highlight your features and express your personal style. Be sure to check out Cassiopeia Gems' collection of stunning jewellery pieces to find the perfect match for your hairstyle.</p>
</div>
</div>
